dStrike (CRWD)\\n * ServiceNow (NOW)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"4a8789e5","parentId":"04844133","timestamp":"2026-05-10T04:30:16.254Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"14b83be8","parentId":"4a8789e5","timestamp":"2026-05-10T04:30:34.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants me to analyze 21 stocks from the list they provided. Let me check if there's any prior analysis context first.\n\nThe list includes:\n1. Energy & Power: CEG, BE, VST, NEE (4)\n2. Compute Silicon: NVDA, AMD, INTC, ARM (4)\n3. Memory & Storage: MU, WDC, STX, 000660.KS (4)\n4. Networking: AVGO, MRVL, ANET (3)\n5. Systems & Cooling: VRT, SMCI, ETN, 2317.TW (4)\n\n\n6. Models & MLOps: MSFT, META, GOOGL (3)\n7. Agentic AI & Apps: PLTR, CRWD, NOW (3)\n\nThat adds up to 25 companies total, so I'm missing something from the original 21 stock request.\n\nLet me reconsider what's been analyzed already—the VOO/QQQ/VTI holdings are core ETFs, and Jo mentioned some stocks like NVDA and PLTR have been discussed recently. I need to figure out which 21 stocks Jo wants me to focus on, since the seven-layer framework contains more than that. Looking at the memory and transcript history to identify which 21 stocks have already been covered—I need to narrow down from the full list of 25+ companies mentioned across these categories to determine what remains unanalyzed.","thinkingSignature":"6b9326208e5ccf7f0983857a01da3fdaec4bdda5f7b5377c50e3dfa5c16b5263"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n先查記憶體與歷史對話確認已分析的範圍。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_33z3kbnu04v1_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"corpus":"all","query":"財報分析 NVDA AMD MU VRT 分析"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_33z3kbnu04v1_2","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"includeDerivedTitles":true,"includeLastMessage":true,"limit":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15903,"output":393,"cacheRead":608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16904,"cost":{"input":0.0047709,"output":0.00047159999999999997,"cacheRead":0.000036479999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00527898}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timesta