",\n      \"score\": 0.89053273\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5f755c0775f1c038\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNvidia earnings preview: Fiscal Q1 2026 | S&P Global\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5f755c0775f1c038\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.spglobal.com/market-intelligence/en/news-insights/research/2025/05/nvidia-earnings-preview-fiscal-q1-2026\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b94b547df509acd8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAccording to Visible Alpha consensus, total revenues of $43.2 billion are expected for Fiscal Q1 2026. Overall revenue growth continues to be driven by optimism\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b94b547df509acd8\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.8900749\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d66ab2180bdedf0b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNVIDIA 2026 Q1 Financial Results\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d66ab2180bdedf0b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://morethanmoore.substack.com/p/nvidia-2026-q1-financial-results\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"89e2e4054c710f66\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n# NVIDIA 2026 Q1 Financial Results. [![Image 1: More Than Moore](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!IeZL!,w_40,h_40,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd0bddc7f-1935-4d0b-bf60-6934bb4f043a_610x610.png)](https://morethanmoore.substack.com/). # [More Than Moore](https://morethanmoore.substack.com/). # NVIDIA 2026 Q1 Financial Results. [![Image 2: Ryan Smith's avatar](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ecHn!,w_36,h_36,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a124a1d-8470-4e15-a97c-abbb422e18f6_2466x2466.jpeg)](https://substack.com/@ryansmithat)[![Image 3: Dr. Ian Cutress's avatar](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!je3E!,w_36,h_36,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbe0dbaa-35c1-4086-899d-f4539a834215_773x773.png)](https://substack.com/@morethanmoore). [Ryan Smith](https://substack.com/@ryansmithat) and [Dr. Ian Cutress](https://substack.com/@morethanmoore). [NVDA 0.00%↑](https://substack.com/search/%24NVDA). As we look to close the book on the calendar year Q1 earnings season, we once again find ourselves closing things out with NVIDIA. The company’s quirky earnings calendar, which saw the company wrap up the first quarter of its _2026_ fiscal year on April 27 th of 2025, is both a boon and a bane for the company. ![Image 4: User's avatar](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!je3E!,w_64,h_64,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffbe0dbaa-35c1-4086-899d-f4539a834215_773x773.png). ## Continue reading this post for free, courtesy of Dr. Ian Cutress. [Claim my free post](https://morethanmoore.substack.com/p/nvidia-2026-q1-financial-results). [Or purchase a paid subscription.](https://morethanmoore.substack.com/subscribe?simple=true&next=https%3A%2F%2Fmorethanmoore.substack.com%2Fp%2Fnvidia-2026-q1-financial-results&utm_source=paywall&utm_medium=web&utm_content=164687194&just_signed_up=falsesimple=true&utm_source=paywall&utm_medium=email&utm_content=164687194&next=https://morethanmoore.substack.com/p/nvidia-2026-q1-financial-results). [![Image 5: Ryan Smith's avatar](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ecHn!,w_52,h_52,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8a124a1d-8470-4e15-a97c-abbb422e18f6_2466x2466.jpeg)](https://substack.com/@ryansmithat?utm_source=byline)A guest post by [Ryan Smith](https://substack.com/@ryansmithat?utm_cam