id it was “going really well.” OpenAI had previously said it would build a 1GW data center using AMD MI450 chips, but no information about where OpenAI, or Meta, will be deploying the initial GPUs has been provided.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bf71bded78379902\">>>","score":0.9999877},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"92d901381c90b585\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAMD Earnings: AI Data Center Explosion! | Q1 2026 Results Analysis\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"92d901381c90b585\">>>","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JcIrvyQHg3Q","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b0987956e4e17cf4\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAMD (NASDAQ: AMD) just dropped its Q1 2026 earnings, and the numbers are massive. Led by CEO Dr. Lisa Su, the chipmaker crushed expectations\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b0987956e4e17cf4\">>>","score":0.9999871},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"117faa9ec4d17363\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAMD Earnings: AI-Driven Data Center Growth Signals New Era Dominance | Trefis\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"117faa9ec4d17363\">>>","url":"https://www.trefis.com/stock/amd/articles2/598792/amd-earnings-ai-driven-data-center-growth-signals-new-era-dominance/2026-05-08","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0da2ce43ce3aef3c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAMD: Advanced Micro Devices logo. Advanced Micro Devices (AMD) reported its 2026 Q1 earnings on 5/5/2026 after market close. The earnings report confirms a significant shift in AMD’s business, with the data center now firmly established as the main growth engine. This is driven by the irreversible trend of AI adoption and the increasing demand for high-performance computing. To better understand how the market might digest these fundamentals, it helps to examine how AMD stock has historically reacted to earnings. The Data Center segment was the primary growth driver, with revenue surging 57% year-over-year to $5.8 billion. Wall S