rowth in the low 20% range. • We expect 2025 NAND bit demand growth to be in the high -teens percentage. • We expect calendar 2026 industry DRAM and NAND bit shipment growth to be. • We expect both DRAM and NAND calendar 2026 industry bit shipments to. • Micron plans to increase our fiscal 2026 capex to approximately $20 billion,. • Cloud Memory Business Unit revenue was a record $5.3 billion and. • Core Data Center Business Unit revenue was a record $2.4 billion and. • Mobile Client Business Unit revenue was a record $ 4.3 billion and.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"17d94a9b0f97f677\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.76888984\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["query","provider","count","tookMs","externalContent","results"]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778387548812}}
{"type":"message","id":"874365d4","parentId":"6d84b69f","timestamp":"2026-05-10T04:32:28.813Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_931a04tap7hn_4","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Constellation Energy CEG Q1 2026 earnings revenue\",\n  \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1908,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"798522542edfbd80\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConstellation Energy Q1 2026 earnings preview - MSN\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"798522542edfbd80\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.msn.com/en-us/money/topstocks/constellation-energy-q1-2026-earnings-preview/ar-AA22IanC\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"abb9fe23df360003\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe consensus EPS Estimate is $2.61 (+22.0% Y/Y) and the consensus Revenue Estimate is $8.71B (+30.2% Y/Y). Over the last 2 years, CEG has beaten EPS estimates\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"abb9fe23df360003\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.96323407\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4502996144b647a0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConstellation Energy (CEG) Earnings Date & Report - Investing.com\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4502996144b647a0\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.investing.com/equities/constellation-energy-earnings\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b6d98899c9223b67\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConstellation Energy (CEG) Earnings Dates & Reports ; Latest Release. Feb 23, 2026 ; EPS / Forecast. 2.30 / 2.31 ; Revenue / Forecast. 6.07B / 4.95B ; EPS Revisions.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b6d98899c9223b67\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.94276565\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"67e140f5721cdf40\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConstellation Energy Stock is Down 13% in 2026: What the Q1 2026 Earnings Must Show  | TIKR.com\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"67e140f5721cdf40\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.tikr.com/blog/constellation-energy-stock-is-down-13-in-2026-what-the-q1-2026-earnings-must-show\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0895b3f26c084dad\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n# Constellation Energy Stock is Down 13% in 2026: What the Q1 2026 Earnings Must Show. The Calpine acquisition fundamentally repriced what Constellation Energy stock is worth on a forward earnings basis, and the Street’s reaction to the March guidance call has not closed that gap yet. EBITDA tells the sharper story here: consensus estimates show CEG’s EBITDA surging from $0.84 billion in Q4 2025 to $2.02 billion in Q1 2026, a 189% year-over-year increase driven directly by Calpine adding its natural gas and geothermal earnings to the combined platform. The catalyst is the Q1 2026 earnings call on May 11: the number to watch is whether Q1 EBITDA tracks toward consensus at $2.02 billion, confirming that the Calpine integration is delivering at the pace the model requires. ***With 20 of 21 analysts bullish on Constellation Energy stock and the May 11 earnings call days away, the window to build a position ahead of a potential catalyst is short: access real-time analyst estimates and price target data on CEG with TIKR for free →***.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0895b3f26c084dad\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9126935\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea3dfd083cd0f8b4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConstellation Energy Earnings Estimates, EPS & Revenue | NASDAQ:CEG | Benzinga\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea3dfd083cd0f8b4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.benzinga.com/quo