2026 Organic Growth Guidance to 10% from 8% at the Midpoint**. * **First quarter sales were up 17% with organic sales growth of 10%, above the high end of the 5-7% guidance range**. * **For full year 2026, earnings per share expected to be between $10.88 and $11.33, up 6% at the midpoint over 2025, and adjusted earnings per share expected to be between $13.05 and $13.50​, up 10% at the midpoint over 2025**. Sales in the quarter were $7.5 billion, a record and up 17% from the first quarter of 2025. Sales for the Electrical Americas segment were a record $3.6 billion, up 20% from the first quarter of 2025. Operating profits were a first quarter record $922 million, up 2% over the first quarter of 2025, and operating margins in the quarter were 25.6%. Sales for the Electrical Global segment were a record $1.9 billion, up 21% from the first quarter of 2025.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ebeb69001340896d\">>>","score":0.829285}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778387565475}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b9317a5","parentId":"d9ca1c71","timestamp":"2026-05-10T04:32:57.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I'm getting solid data. Let me search for a few more stocks that are important - Alphabet GOOGL, and some others like Supermicro, Western Digital, etc.","thinkingSignature":"4295afe18dd17f84c66da2ee7237722727a67dd7547aca5db28a7bb1fcc3faca"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pzmhd93ygsp1_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"Alphabet GOOGL Q1 2026 earnings revenue Google Cloud AI"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pzmhd93ygsp1_2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"Western Digital WDC Q2 2026 earnings revenue AI storage"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pzmhd93ygsp1_3","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"ServiceNow NOW Q1 2026 earnings revenue AI agents"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pzmhd93ygsp1_4","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"CrowdStrike CRWD Q1 2026 earnings revenue AI cybersecurity"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pzmhd93ygsp1_5","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"Super Micro Computer SMCI Q3 2026 earnings revenue audit"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13826,"output":253,"cacheRead":55744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69823,"cost":{"input":0.0041478,"output":0.0003036,"cacheRead":0.00334464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007796040000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778387565478,"responseId":"064f3d70037eb0e5edefa17f4b8b901e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d0c64a6","parentId":"8b9317a5","timestamp":"2026-05-10T04:33:01.593Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pzmhd93ygsp1_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Alphabet GOOGL Q1 2026 earnings revenue Google Cloud AI\",\n  \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1761,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b6eb14dfa841652a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlphabet Q1 2026 earnings: Google Cloud revenue up 63% - Quartz\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b6eb14dfa841652a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://qz.com/alphabet-google-cloud-earnings-q1-2026-042926?.tsrc=rss\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4f4c77361f90c2c0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGoogle Cloud brought in $20.03 billion in revenue for the quarter, up 63% year over year, with operating income rising to $6.6 billion from $2.2\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4f4c77361f90c2c0\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999858\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"151efcca46e47117\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlphabet (GOOGL) Q1 2026 Earnings Breakdown: AI & Cloud Drive ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"151efcca46e47117\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h6MuGS51Iic\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2823f7c7d79b8c48\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n... AI investment a brilliant move or a risky bet?* **#Alphabet #GOOGL #Earnings #GoogleCloud #AI #StockMarket #Investing #TechStocks #SundarPichai*\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2823f7c7d79b8c48\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999727\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0dfebc2515d96f59\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGoogle Profit Jumps 81% as Cloud Business Booms - WSJ\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0dfebc2515d96f59\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.wsj.com/tech/alphabet-earnings-q1-2026-googl-stock-283553bc\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d68746dff8a9a621\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlphabet reported a 22% surge in first-quarter revenue to about $110 billion, fueled by its cloud business and AI race. Shares in Alphabet rose\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d68746dff8a9a621\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999374\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cb4d0b0d9b00cf03\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGoogle Cloud revenue is now 18% of Alphabet's business ... - Fortune\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cb4d0b0d9b00cf03\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://fortune.com/2026/04/29/google-earnings-cloud-ai/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9edef5d2a01c521a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEver since [Google](https://fortune.com/company/alphabet/) was founded in 1998, search has been the core of the company’s identity. The company’s cloud-computing business was the undisputed star of parent company Alphabet’s [first-quarter earnings](http://chrome-extension://efaidnbmnnnibpcajpcglclefindmkaj/https://s206.q4cdn.com/479360582/files/doc_financials/2026/q1/2026q1-alphabet-earnings-release.pdf), posting an eye-popping 63% revenue growth from the prior year, for a total of $20 billion. [AI is of course what’s driving the booming growth](https://fortune.com/2026/04/29/microsoft-meta-google-ai-capex-spending-billions/) in Google’s cloud business, as CEO Sundar Pichai and other company executives noted on the earnings call. Advertising has always been the center of gravity for Google, with its high-margin and recession-proof search ads at the top of a mountain that includes [YouTube](https://fortune.com/company/youtube/) video ads, display ads that Google distributes to other sites, and ads that appear in Google’s portfolio of popular properties like Gmail and Maps. The cloud business is run by enterprise sales people in suits like [Cloud boss Thomas Kurian](https://fortune.com/2025/12/23/google-cloud-ceo-thomas-kurian-ai-energy-tpu-battle/?utm_source=search&utm_medium=suggested_search&utm_campaign=search_link_clicks), an [Oracle](https://fortune.com/company/oracle/) veteran. By [Jake Angelo](https://fortune.com/author/jake-angelo/)May 7, 2026. Weeks later, construction began](https://fortune.com/2026/05/06/ai-data-center-michigan-saline-politics-farmland/?itm_source=parsely-api). [U.S. Treasury will have to borrow $2 trillion this year just to continue functioning—more than $166 billion every month](https://fortune.com/2026/05/07/treasury-expected-to-borrow-2-trillion-omb-cbo-estimates/?itm_source=parsely-api).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9edef5d2a01c521a\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99990165\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0e9d8364a0cb6cd7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlphabet revenue tops expectations on record quarter for cloud unit\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0e9d8364a0cb6cd7\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.reuters.com/business/alphabets-cloud-unit-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-strong-ai-demand-2026-04-29/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d3b8c70f62bdc85a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n[Skip to main content](https://www.reuters.com/business/alphabets-cloud-unit-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-strong-ai-demand-2026-04-29/#main-content). *   [Business](https://www.reuters.com/business/). ## [Browse Business](https://www.reuters.com/business/). *   [Take Five](https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/). April 29 (Reuters) - Alphabet [(GOOGL.O), opens new tab](https://www.reuters.com/markets/companies/GOOGL.O) topped Wall Street estimates for quarterly revenue on Wednesday, as enterprise spending on artificial intelligence delivered the best quarter of reported growth for its cloud unit yet. Its decision to lease TPUs to cloud customers helped [drive growth](https://www.reuters.com/business/ai-turned-google-cloud-also-ran-into-alphabets-growth-driver-2025-10-31/) for Google Cloud, but the company had held ​off on directly selling those chips until now. Ashkenazi raised this year's forecast to between $180 billion and $190 billion, a $5 billion bump from ‌what she announced [last quarter](https://www.reuters.com/business/google-parent-alphabet-forecasts-sharp-surge-2026-capital-spending-2026-02-04/), ⁠and said that Alphabet was planning another significant increase in 2027. Revenue at Amazon Web Services [jumped](https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amazon-beats-quarterly-cloud-growth-estimates-2026-04-29/) 28% to $37.6 billion in the first quarter, compared with analysts' average estimate of a 25.1% increase to $36.6 billion, according to LSEG. Our Standards: [The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles., opens new tab](https://www.thomsonreuters.com/en/about-us/trust-principles.html). *   [](https://www.reuters.com/business/alphabets-cloud-unit-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-strong-ai-demand-2026-04-29/hoodieonveshti). *   [](https://www.reuters.com/business/alphabets-cloud-unit-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-strong-ai-demand-2026-04-29/kenrick.01). ## [Business](https://www.reuters.com/business/). *   [Home](https://www.reuters.com/). *   [Home](https://www.reuters.com/). *   [Business](https://www.reuters.com/business/). *   [](https://www.facebook.com/Reuters). *   [](https://www.instagram.com/Reuters). [See here for a list of exchanges and delays.](https://www.reuters.com/info-pages/disclaimer/).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d3b8c70f62bdc85a\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99937373\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Alphabet GOOGL Q1 2026 earnings 