AAP revenues of $3.11 billion exceeded the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 5.7%.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8e95be47a489ef2b\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99999666\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2766cc4ad912493c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSeagate Q3 2026 earnings beat, raises Q4 forecast on AI demand\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2766cc4ad912493c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://qz.com/seagate-earnings-ai-storage-demand-forecast-042926\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"11bc01a1bdcd0da2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe data storage company posted $3.11 billion in Q3 revenue and projected $3.45 billion for the current quarter, well above analyst estimates ·\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"11bc01a1bdcd0da2\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999937\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b526d42c41fb79e7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSeagate (STX) Had a Blowout Q3. The AI Storage Bull Case Is ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b526d42c41fb79e7\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.tipranks.com/news/seagate-stx-had-a-blowout-q3-the-ai-storage-bull-case-is-building\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"67cd5be493a8e648\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe Q3 FY2026 earnings report highlighted a business consistently beating estimates. Revenue rose 44% year-over-year to $3.1 billion against a\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"67cd5be493a8e648\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999924\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"10d27e28857e2cc2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSeagate Technology plc Q3 2026 Earnings Recap | AllInvestView\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"10d27e28857e2cc2\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.allinvestview.com/earnings/STX/q3-2026/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0b49afbd377c38b5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n# Seagate Technology plc Q3 2026 Earnings Recap. STX Q3 2026  April 29, 2026. Seagate shares surged 8% after the company’s fiscal Q3 report, as revenue jumped 44% year-over-year, gross margins hit all-time highs, and management issued notably upbeat guidance. Investors responded positively to record free cash flow and strong commentary on accelerating storage demand tied to AI and cloud infrastructure buildout. This summary was generated by AI from the official earnings call transcript and is provided for informational purposes only. For the complete transcript and financial data, visit STX on AllInvestView. ## Also Reported on April 29, 2026. AB · Q1 2026  Amkor Technology, Inc. AMKR · Q1 2026  ArcBest Corporation. Track Seagate Technology plc in your portfolio with real-time analytics, dividend tracking, and more. AllInvestView is not a registered investment advisor or broker/dealer, and the information presented here is for educational and informational purposes only.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0b49afbd377c38b5\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999844\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d7afa0dfd1e60cca\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSTX Q3-2026 Earnings Call\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d7afa0dfd1e60cca\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.alphaspread.com/security/nasdaq/stx/investor-relations/earnings-call/q3-2026\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a2b160d02872b803\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n**Strong quarter:** Seagate said March quarter revenue was $3.1 billion, up 44% year over year, with record gross margin, more than doubled operating income, and free cash flow close to $1 billion. **HAMR ramp:** Seagate said Mozaic 4 is now shipping, two of the world’s largest cloud providers are qualified on the 4+ terabyte per disk product, and the company expects Mozaic 4 to become a majority of HAMR exabyte shipments exiting calendar 2026. Mozaic 4 began revenue shipments in late March, two large cloud customers are qualified on the 4+ terabyte per disk product, and the company expects Mozaic 4 to be the majority of HAMR exabyte shipments exiting calendar 2026. The company said most of its nearline capacity is allocated over the next four quarters and that build-to-order contracts for fiscal 2027 have been finalized, giving it strong visibility into mix, volume and pricing.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a2b160d02872b803\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99996054\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Seagate STX Q3 2026 earnings revenue AI storage","provider":"tavily","count":5,"tookMs":1537,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"tavily","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d82e5333d397d483\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSTX Q3 Earnings Top Estimates, Revenues Up on AI-Led Storage Demand - April 29, 2026 - Zacks.com\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d82e5333d397d483\">>>","url":"https://www.zacks.com/stock/news/2910946/stx-q3-earnings-top-estimates-revenues-up-on-ai-led-storage-demand","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8e95be47a489ef2b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWe use cookies to understand how you use our site and to improve your experience. By pressing \"Accept All\" or closing out of this banner, you consent to the use of all cookies and similar technologies and the sharing of information they collect with third parties. In addition, whether you \"Accept All,\" Deny Optional,\" click the X or otherwise continue to use the site, you accept our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service, revised from time to time. **Seagate Technology Holdings plc** (STX Quick QuoteSTX  -  Free Report) reported third-quarter fiscal 2026 non-GAAP earnings of $4.10 per share, beating the Zacks Consensus Estimate of $3.50 and exceeding the high end of management’s guidance of $3.40 (